So excited to officially announce on here that there's going to be an #agirlinprogress book out in the world in May 2020! 🎉 It's been a lot of blood, sweat, tears and coffees getting this thing done, but the cover is finally here and im in love.😍
When I started the blog just under 2 years ago, I wasn't sure where it would go. I just knew I wanted to create a space that celebrates women who are perfectly imperfect and are working on themselves FOR themselves
.
 #progressoverperfection takes this same approach and applies it to productivity. It's all about teaching you to work smarter not harder, and to get sh*t done without working yourself into the ground or getting burnt out.
.
It's officially our on May 5 next year, but stay tuned for pre-orders to be one of the first to get your hands on it! ✨

Here at A Girl In Progress, we believe a great handbag is more than just a fashion statement or status symbol. It's a powerful vessel that allows you to carry the essentials you need to conquer your day and dominate your to-do list. 💪
.
That's why we've teamed up with the legends at @shopvestirsi to give away TWO of their gorgeous, Italian leather handbags — the ultimate work bag, The Tonia, and her adorable little sister, The Brigitte. .
Entries are available worldwide and are open from today to the 1st January. You gotta be in it to win it, so head to the link in bio or swipe up in our stories to enter! .
